explain sequence of steps to go from raw scans to animation :

1- Add mti data to scans with putmtidata.pl

2- Get gmaps images with getmaps.pl

3- Generate plots with plotlogs.pl

4- Animate plots with animatelogs.pl

for ivy:
libio-socket-multicast-perl
svn co http://svn.tls.cena.fr/svn/ivy/ivy-perl/trunk (perl Makefile.pl;make;sudo make install)
libterm-readline-perl-perl (for ivyprobe)
